        <li id="ref2">Pasquali, A., et al. (2019). Projected phase space zones and mean infall times.</li>
        <li id="ref3">Rhee, J., et al. (2017). Phase-space analysis of cluster satellites.</li>
        <li id="ref4">Yang, X., et al. (2007). Halo velocity dispersion calibration.</li>
        <li id="ref5">Dou, H., Yu, H. (2025). "Estimating infall times of galaxies around clusters." <em>A&amp;A</em> 699, A95.</li>
        <li id="ref6">Kim, K. J., et al. (2023). "A gradual decline of star formation since cluster infall." <em>ApJ</em> 955, 32.</li>
        <li id="ref7">Sampaio, V. M., et al. (2021). Observational application of PPS-calibrated infall times.</li>
        <li id="ref8">Oxland, M., et al. (2024). Environmental processing of cluster satellites.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="page-tags">
      <strong>Tags:</strong>
      <WikiLink slug="pages/tag_observational_techniques" text="Observational Techniques" />
